l>([[Florence and the Machine]])</small>\n| Eliminated\n|- \n| 7\n| Alena Shirmanova\n| \"[[Theme from New York, New York]]\" <small>([[Frank Sinatra]])</small>\n| Eliminated\n|- \n| 8\n| Karol\u00edna P\u0159ibylov\u00e1\n| \"[[I See Fire]]\" <small>([[Ed Sheeran]])</small>\n| Eliminated\n|- \n| 9\n| Nikol Kassell\n| \"[[Love on Top]]\" <small>([[Beyonc\u00e9]])</small>\n| Eliminated\n|- style=\"background:#ccc;\" \n| 10\n| '''[[Emma Drobn\u00e1]]'''\n| \"[[Your Song]]\" <small>([[Elton John]])</small>\n| '''Advanced'''\n|}\n\n===Finalist===\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n||'''Contestant'''\n|  style=\"width:50px;\"|'''Age at time of show'''\n||'''Hometown'''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Czech Republic|size=15px}} Dalibor Slep\u010d\u00edk\n| 15\n| [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]], [[Czech Republic]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Czech Republic|size=15px}} Daniel K\u0159i\u017eka\n| 20\n| [[Brumovice (B\u0159eclav District)|Brumovice]], [[Czech Republic]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Czech Republic|size=15px}} \u0160t\u011bp\u00e1n Urban\n| 17\n| [[Uhersk\u00e9 Hradi\u0161t\u011b]], [[Czech Republic]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Slovakia|size=15px}} Pavol Kovali\u010dek\n| 19\n| [[De\u017eerice]], [[Slovakia]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Czech Republic|size=15px}} Sabina Slep\u010d\u00edkov\u00e1\n| 23\n| [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]], [[Czech Republic]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Slovakia|size=15px}} Barbora Hazuchov\u00e1\n| 17\n| [[Liptovsk\u00fd Mikul\u00e1\u0161]], [[Slovakia]] \n|-\n| {{flagicon|Slovakia|size=15px}} [[Emma Drobn\u00e1]]\n| 21\n| [[Nov\u00e9 Mesto nad V\u00e1hom]], [[Slovakia]]  \n|-\n| {{flagicon|Slovakia|size=15px}} Veronika Dani\u0161ov\u00e1\n| 21\n| [[Partiz\u00e1nske]], [[Slovakia]] \n|}\n\n===Finals===\nEight contestants made it to the finals. TOP 8 consists of 1 Slovak boy, 3 Czech boys, 3 Slovak girls and 1 Czech girl. The first single recorded by TOP 8 is cover version of  [[\u010cesko Slovensk\u00e1 SuperStar 2009]] theme song \"Pr\u00edbeh nekon\u010d\u00ed\" (The Story Doesn't End). Every final night has its theme. Audience can vote for contestants from the very beginning of the show, voting ends during result show on the same day.\n\n===Top 8 \u2013 No. 1 Hits===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ \n! scope=\"col\"| Order\n! scope=\"col\"| Contestant\n! scope=\"col\"| Song <small>(original artist)</small>\n! scope=\"col\"| Result\n|- \n| 1\n| Dalibor Slep\u010d\u00edk\n| \"[[Billie Jean]]\" <small>([[Michael Jackson]])</small>\n| Safe\n|- \n| 2\n| Sabina Slep\u010d\u00edkov\u00e1\n| \"[[All About That Bass]]\" <small>([[Meghan Trainor]])</small>\n| Safe\n|- style=\"background:#ccc;\"\n| 3\n| '''Daniel K\u0159i\u017eka'''\n| \"[[You're Beautiful]]\" <small>([[James Blunt]])</small>\n| '''Eliminated'''\n|- style=\"background:#ddd;\"\n| 4\n| Barbora Hazuchov\u00e1\n| \"[[Titanium (song)|Titanium]]\" <small>([[Sia Furler|Sia]])</small>\n| Bottom 3\n|-style=\"background:#ddd;\"\n| 5\n| \u0160t\u011bp\u00e1n Urban\n| \"[[I'm Yours (Jason Mraz song)|I'm Yours]]\" <small>([[Jason Mraz]])</small>\n| Bottom 3\n|-\n| 6\n| [[Emma Drobn\u00e1]]\n| \"[[Habits (Tove Lo song)|Habits]]\" <small>([[Tove Lo]])</small>\n| Safe\n|-\n| 7\n| Pavol Kovali\u010dek\n| \"[[Demons (Imagine Dragons song)|Demons]]\" <small>([[Imagine Dragons]])</small>\n| Safe\n|-\n| 8\n| Veronika Dani\u0161ov\u00e1\n| \"[[No One (Alicia Keys song)|No One]]\" <small>([[Alicia Keys]])</small>\n| Safe\n|}\n\n===Top 7 \u2013 Movies Night===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ \n! scope=\"col\"| Order\n! scope=\"col\"| Contestant\n! scope=\"col\"| Song <small>(original artist)</small>\n! scope=\"col\"| Movie\n! scope=\"col\"| Result\n|- \n| 1\n| Dalibor Slep\u010d\u00edk\n| \"Do v\u011b\u017e\u00ed\" <small>([[Waldemar Matu\u0161ka]])</small>\n| ''[[A Night at Karlstein]]''\n| Safe\n|- style=\"background:#ddd;\"\n| 2\n| Sabina Slep\u010d\u00edkov\u00e1\n| \"[[It Must Have Been Love]]\" <small>([[Roxette]])</small>\n| ''[[Pretty Woman]]''\n| Bottom 3\n|- style=\"background:#ccc;\"\n| 3\n| '''Barbora Hazuchov\u00e1'''\n| \"[[Skyfall (Adele song)|Skyfall]]\" <small>([[Adele]])</small>\n| ''[[Skyfall]]''\n| '''Eliminated'''\n|-style=\"background:#ddd;\"\n| 4\n| \u0160t\u011bp\u00e1n Urban \n| \"[[Hallelujah (Leonard Cohen song)|Hallelujah]]\" <small>([[Leonard Cohen]])</small>\n| ''[[Shrek]]''\n| Bottom 3\n|-\n| 5\n| [[Emma Drobn\u00e1]]\n| \"\u010cere\u0161ne\" <small>([[Zuzana Kronerov\u00e1]])</small>\n| ''[[Cosy Dens]]''\n| Safe\n|-\n| 6\n| Pavol Kovali\u010dek\n| \"[[I Don't Want to Miss a Thing]]\" <small>([[Aerosmith]])</small>\n| ''[[Armageddon (1998 film)|Armageddon]]''\n| Safe\n|-\n| 7\n| Veronika Dani\u0161ov\u00e1\n| \"[[Let It Go (Disney song)|Let It Go]]\" <small>([[Idina Menzel]])</small>\n| ''[[Frozen (2013 film)|Frozen]]''\n| Safe\n|}\n\n* '''Group performance''': \nTOP 7 - Girls: \"[[A Little Party Never Killed Nobody (All We Got)|A Little Party Never Killed Nobody]]\" <small>([[Fergie (singer)|Fergie]])</small><br>\nTOP 7 - Boys: \"[[Oh, Pretty Woman]]\" <small>([[Roy Orbison]])</small>\n\n===Top 6 \u2013 Czech and Slovak Hits===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ \n! scope=\"col\"| Order\n! scope=\"col\"| Contestant\n! scope=\"col\"| Song <small>(original artist)</small>\n! scope=\"col\"| Result\n|- \n| 1\n| Dalibor Slep\u010d\u00edk\n|  \"P\u00e1r p\u0159\u00e1tel sta\u010d\u00ed m\u00edt\" <small>([[Michal David]])</small>\n| Safe\n|-style=\"background:#ddd;\"\n| 2\n| Sabina Slep\u010d\u00edkov\u00e1\n| \"Te\u010f kr\u00e1lovnou jsem j\u00e1\" <small>([[Monika Absolonov\u00e1]])</small>\n| Bottom 3\n|- style=\"background:#ccc;\"\n| 3\n| '''\u0160t\u011bp\u00e1n Urban'''\n| \"Chci zas v tob\u011b sp\u00e1t\" <small>(Lucie)</small>\n| '''Saved'''\n|-\n| 4\n| [[Emma Drobn\u00e1]]\n| \"Pokoj v du\u0161i\" <small>([[Jana Kirschner]])</small>\n| Safe\n|-\n| 5\n| Pavol Kovali\u010dek\n| \"Zbohom bu\u010f, lipo